ed approaches to deriving CB properties could be a powerful tool\nfor application to the much larger CB samples expected to result from future\nsurveys.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 19 Feb 2020 04:35:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-04-01"}
