 arousal or valence information can help to improve the classification\naccuracy. In addition, the information of positive/negative valence boosts the\nclassification accuracy to a higher degree on this dataset.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 19 Feb 2020 07:23:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-02-20"}
