onical power law dN/dE ~\nE^-2, suggesting that magnetic energy release in J0331-27 -- and possibly in\nall L dwarfs -- takes place predominantly in the form of giant flares.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 19 Feb 2020 09:32:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-02-20"}
